cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use JOREK, please cite the overview article and relevant prior works (see references and JOREK code website https://www.jorek.eu/)."
title: "JOREK: Non-linear 3D extended magneto-hydrodynamic and hybrid fluid-kinetic code for fusion plasma simulations"
version: "v2.26.02"  # Adjust to current version
abstract: "JOREK simulates non-linear lage scale transient plasma instabilities (and more) in magnetically confined tokamak and stellarator plasmas."
